{"tid":787901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麥格理︰不是貿易戰 而是樓市","createTime":"2018-08-21T05:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T05:42:48.000Z","uid":153236,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"53f2225ef0f50feab12dbdf72a0f871ddcaf5335","tid":787901,"uid":153236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:05:07.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普﹙Donald Trump﹚追擊下，中美貿易戰已令中國人仔股市齊插水，但麥格理首席經濟師Larry Hu則警告，中國熾熱樓市的風險才是致命傷，這對內地經濟帶來的危機，遠大於中美貿易戰。<br />\n<br />\nLarry Hu認為未來一年中國經濟的最大風險來自樓市，尤其他正關注中國二、三線城市樓價炒高後的回落，以及新建樓房減產的情況。<strong>當內地樓市下跌，這將對地方政府的收入、銀行借貸、企業投資帶來重大的負面影響，從而拖垮整個中國經濟</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n根據中國國家統計局數據，內地樓價已連升超過3年，這是自2008年以來最長升勢。上周，二線城市南京，已宣佈禁止企業購買住宅物業，以防止投機行為。不過，市場似乎仍然偏向相信內地樓市有上升空間，因為中央政府仍徘徊在收緊和寬鬆的樓市政策之間，為怕樓價下滑帶來經濟風險，因而資金仍選擇繼續流向樓市，而非內需領域。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180821/58588900\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180821%2F58588900&d=ogEaDYtAKoEXuTJTj9L6UgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=abc86aa1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180821%2F58588900&h=665b2072\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180821/58588900</a>"},{"pid":"8f1c5f8eab3f8921dd75b70ff0498ee97a2f7990","tid":787901,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:06:19.000Z","msg":"透過貿易戰升高支那失業率<br />\n<br />\n截斷支那人供樓能力"},{"pid":"ef1029bf76989de4e84ba1438fc38bed515b268b","tid":787901,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:06:57.000Z","msg":"中國有剛衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1109e0efaac6878661dba469da86cd5bfc15413c","tid":787901,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:07:09.000Z","msg":"支那樓市有無出mini bond<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa11a7b2acc3bae71298aa8c864d860131ce2aa2","tid":787901,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:38:32.000Z","msg":"咁多年工廠開發 依家就算d人想種田都唔得啦d土壤水源咁毒"},{"pid":"95a8973664405de4dbb3953a05b759589e9cddd9","tid":787901,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef1029bf76989de4e84ba1438fc38bed515b268b","tid":787901,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:06:57.000Z","msg":"中國有剛衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:40:22.000Z","msg":"肛衰"},{"pid":"fe461efc4e693c71fecc360765d7fcb20a9e11b1","tid":787901,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:42:48.000Z","msg":"呢篇野cnbc都睇過<br />\n又係個華裔記者寫嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}